      <span class="tag">Comparison</span>
      <h1>Sony WH-1000XM5 vs Sennheiser Momentum 4: Which Is Better in 2026?</h1>
      <div class="meta">Updated June 2026 · 9 min read</div>
    </div>

    <nav class="toc">
      <h2>Table of Contents</h2>
      <ol>
        <li><a href="#overview">Overview</a></li>
        <li><a href="#specs">Specs Comparison</a></li>
